    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Ace
    Represents an Ace card, a subclass of Standard with a rank of 1.
    ActionException
    Exception thrown when an invalid action occurs in the game.
    Board
    Represents the game board for the Jackaroo game.
    BoardManager
    Defines the contract for managing communication with the Board class.
    Burner
    Represents the Burner card in the wild card category.
    CannotDiscardException
    Exception thrown when a discard action cannot be performed in the game.
    CannotFieldException
    Exception thrown when a field action cannot be performed in the game.
    Card
    Represents an abstract in-game card used in the Jackaroo game.
    Cell
    Represents a cell on the Jackaroo board.
    CellType
    Represents the possible types of cells on the Jackaroo game board.
    Colour
    Represents the four possible colours of the marbles in the Jackaroo game.
    CPU
    The CPU class represents a computer-controlled player in the game.
    Deck
    The Deck class is responsible for managing the card pool in the Jackaroo game.
    Five
    Represents the Five card in a standard deck.
    Four
    Represents the Four card in a standard deck.
    Game
    The Game class represents the main engine of the Jackaroo game.
    GameException
    An abstract class that represents a game-specific exception.
    GameManager
    The GameManager interface provides methods for interacting with the main game logic.
    IllegalDestroyException
     
    IllegalMovementException
    Exception thrown when an illegal movement action is attempted in the game.
    IllegalSwapException
    Exception thrown when an illegal swap action is attempted in the game.
    InvalidCardException
    Exception thrown when an invalid card selection is made in the game.
    InvalidMarbleException
    Exception thrown when an invalid marble selection is made in the game.
    InvalidSelectionException
    Exception thrown when an invalid selection is made in the game.
    Jack
    Represents the Jack card in a standard deck.
    King
    Represents a King card, a subclass of Standard with a rank of 13.
    Marble
    Represents a marble in the Jackaroo game.
    Player
    Represents a player in the Jackaroo game, holding a hand of cards, marbles, and managing the selected card and marbles for play.
    Queen
    Represents the Queen card in a standard deck.
    SafeZone
    Represents a SafeZone on the Jackaroo game board.
    Saver
    Represents the Saver card in the wild card category.
    Seven
    Represents the Seven card in a standard deck.
    SplitOutOfRangeException
    Exception thrown when a split operation exceeds the allowed range.
    Standard
    Represents a standard playing card with a specific rank and suit.
    Suit
    Enum representing the four suits of standard playing cards in the Jackaroo game.
    Ten
    Represents the Ten card in a standard deck.
    Wild
    Represents an abstract wild card in the Jackaroo game.
